posts.title: Standard & Poor's mejora la calificación crediticia de Endesa
posts.text:
Standard & Poor's mejora la calificación crediticia de Endesa ENDESA DEUDA   La fachada de la sede de Standard & Poor's en Nueva York, Estados Unidos. EFE/Archivo 
Madrid, 7 dic (EFE).- La agencia de calificación de riesgos Standard & Poor's (S&P) ha mejorado la nota de la deuda a largo plazo de Endesa de BBB (aprobado) con perspectiva positiva a BBB+ (aprobado alto) con perspectiva estable, ha comunicado hoy la empresa a la Comisión Nacional del Mercado de Valores (CNMV). 
S&P ha mantenido la calificación crediticia a corto plazo de Endesa en A-2 (equivalente a un notable). 
La revisión al alza de la nota de Endesa está incluida en un informe sobre Enel, principal accionista de la eléctrica española, que la agencia de calificación publicó ayer, miércoles. 
En el informe, S&P elevó también la nota de Enel de aprobado a aprobado alto.

posts.author: Penalope
posts.text:
Hi,
Welcome to Google Search and Assistant Help Forum.
For Gmail: The only account recovery option Google provides starts at https://accounts.google.com/signin/recovery / https://support.google.com/accounts/troubleshooter/2402620 (an account can not be recovered by posting here or contacting Google). Submitting more accurate answers and using a known computer/IP-address will help. This post provides an overview of how account recovery works (you NEED to read this) https://productforums.google.com/forum/#!category-topic/gmail/SzwFXkqLvr0 and this article provides many more details on the process (you SHOULD read this) http://gmailaccountrecovery.blogspot.com/
Then go visit the Gmail Help Forum located at https://productforums.google.com/forum/#!forum/gmail .
For Yahoo, visit their help forum located at https://forums.yahoo.net/t5/Yahoo-Help-Community/ct-p/english . A similar URL located at https://forums.yahoo.net/t5/Password-and-sign-in/Recovering-account/m-p/384358 .
For Facebook, visit their help forum located at https://www.facebook.com/help/community . A similar URL located at https://www.facebook.com/help/213395615347144 and https://www.facebook.com/login/identify?ctx=recover (account recovery).
Penalope

posts.text:
Offensive Player of the Year - Braintree's Billy Silvia Tuesday Dec 5, 2017 at 1:53 PM Dec 6, 2017 at 10:39   
Offensive Player of the Year: Billy Silvia, Jr., Braintree 
As a junior, Silvia is already one of the most versatile players in the state. Silvia played running back, linebacker, kicker and was a returning for the Wamps. In total, he finished with 15 touchdowns and nearly broke Braintree’s single-season point record. Paired with quarterback Zach Harris, who ran for over 1,000 yards, Braintree had a lethal combination in the backfield. Silvia already is one of the best players in the area and should be in store for a super senior season. 
Honorable mention: Abel Lopes Jr. (Scituate), Nick Lane (Pembroke), Zach Harris (Braintree) 
Football Power Rankings are decided with the help of several factors: record, strength of schedule, performance against teams and margin of victory. The public schools in our coverage area include: Abington, Braintree, Carver, Cohasset, Hanover, Hingham, Marshfield, Norwell, Pembroke, Plymouth North, Plymouth South, Rockland, Scituate, Silver Lake and Weymouth. posts.text:
Helsinki Published: 07/12/2017 Deadline: 05/01/2018 
We’re looking for an experienced Drupal Developer to join us at our Helsinki office. If you’re interested in usability and user experience, and you're looking for new challenges in the world of Drupal, we'd love to hear from you. EXPERIENCED DRUPAL DEVELOPER 
Who are we looking for? You have experience with common Web technologies like HTML5, CSS & javascript You can independently create responsive design solutions You know how to work with different versions of Drupal You are interested in and love to focus on the experience of users of your solutions You have the courage to suggest new solutions, but also to ask for help when you need it You’re comfortable with both team work and independent work You are fluent in written and spoken English 
We are looking for people who love their job and are passionate about it. With us you get to do your work with likely minded professionals. We are focused on helping our people develop to the fullest of their abilities. 
We offer a position in a rapidly growing company with great career opportunities and a competitive salary. Your work will be challenging, often changing on a short notice, but never boring. In addition to the nice architectural atmosphere at our downtown Helsinki office, you would also be enjoying the company of our experienced and passionate developers as your teammates. 
If this sounds like you, send us a message with your CV attached with it. Projects you have worked on are a great way of telling about yourself. Links to LinkedIn and GitHub profiles are greatly appreciated but not a must. Please include your monthly salary request as well! 
Send your application to rekryhelsinki@sangre.fi with Drupal Developer as the subject line. Apply
